    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到政治正确的终极讽刺！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>做好准备，迎接一场爆笑又冒犯的体验，对抗那些“白左”疯子和他们荒谬至极的意识形态！</strong><br><br><strong>彻底摧毁政治正确的“白左”企业压迫者，让他们灰飞烟灭！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096230/extras/d7711d86e67d34f086f320d392201440.avif?t=1770592454\" width=620 height=96 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于游戏：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《狗根斯坦》的故事发生在一个被暴君寡头“王子”所统治的世界里，他残酷地消灭了一切传统势力和反“白左”思想。</strong><br><br><strong>所有反“白左”者都被处理成一堆排泄物——彻底的疯狂！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096230/extras/002aae1ffdf887dfc8f5b371b3a35c82.poster.avif?t=1770592454\" width=608 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096230/extras/002aae1ffdf887dfc8f5b371b3a35c82.webm?t=1770592454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096230/extras/002aae1ffdf887dfc8f5b371b3a35c82.mp4?t=1770592454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时机已到——是时候反击了！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>唯有传奇狗头挺身而出，对抗寡头王子及其“白左”傀儡！</strong><br><br><strong>加入狗头，在这款前所未有的快节奏复古FPS中奋战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096230/extras/0353b2e41839453e5106aef93360a05c.avif?t=1770592454\" width=620 height=96 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>消灭“白左”疯子，炸毁他们政治正确的“白左”帝国！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扮演传奇狗头！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典老派射击游戏，灵感源自90年代最佳FPS！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式体验：探索监狱、“白左”城市、工厂等场景！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古像素风画面！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>震撼的合成器浪潮风格原声音乐！</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极端暴力+爆笑对白！</strong></p></li></ul>",
